Uludağ.title: Uludağ
Uludağ.byline: Uludağ (pronounced oo loo daa) is a mountain of 2543 m (8343 ft) elevation which gives its name to a national park and ski resort.

Uluṟu-Kata Tjuṯa National Park.title: Uluṟu-Kata Tjuṯa National Park
Uluṟu-Kata Tjuṯa National Park.byline: Uluṟu-Kata Tjuṯa National Park is a park in the Northern Territory of Australia, part of the so-called Red Centre of the continent.
